ized.net%2Fattached%2Finformation%2Fimages%2Fffa91f259cde42df4fda425dd34e29e2.png&h=7e3bf278&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">主線劇情第8章「交錯之炎」登場！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3af36a2d3e1b7eebb4b0e7bfb5023442.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.akamaized.net%2Fattached%2Finformation%2Fimages%2F3af36a2d3e1b7eebb4b0e7bfb5023442.png&h=61bbac08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">「風屬性」角色強化活動舉辦公告</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6aae5ceeda558496c15d40cb40830ba1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdragalialost.akamaized.net%2Fattached%2Finformation%2Fimages%2F6aae5ceeda558496c15d40cb40830ba1.png&h=0e12e0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活動期間內，將持續開放可獲得用來強化風屬性角色的道具之任務「風槌的遺跡（初級/中級/高級）」。<br />\n除此之外，於活動期間內「風槌的遺跡」的每日獎勵報酬將提升成2倍！<br />\n若是購入「2倍獎勵組合包」並於效果期間內，「風槌的遺跡」的每日獎勵將會變成4倍！<br />\n<strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">「花香飄散的夢與友情」</span></strong></span><br />\n傳說召喚「花香飄散的夢與友情」已於2019/04/18 14:00開始舉辦！<br />\n<span style=\"fo